Package hospital.staff

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Administrator
    The Administrator class represents the administrator of the hospital.
    Appointment
    This class represents an appointment in one or more professional's electronic diary.
    BookAppointmentAction
    Represents an appointment deletion in the hospital booking system.
    DeleteAppointmentAction
    Represents an appointment deletion in the hospital booking system.
    ElectronicDiary
    Represents an electronic diary of a professional.
    Professional
    Represents a professional in the hospital staff.
    Staff
    Staff class contains a HashSet of Professionals.
    Task
    Task Class defines a task that a professional can add to their personal task list.
    TaskList
    The TaskList class contains the list of the tasks that professionals can add to their each own personal task list.
    TreatmentType
    Treatment type class defines default treatments available at the hospital.
    User
    Abstract class that defines the user of the system.
    WorkingHours
    Working hours class defines working hours of the Professional.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Role
    Enum that defines available staff roles in the hospital.
